headline: 4 Stocks to Watch in a Dynamic Outpatient Home Health Industry
summary: An aging global population and AI dominance are likely to drive the Zacks Medical - Outpatient and Home Healthcare industry despite the macroeconomic challenges. DVA, EHC, OPCH and ADUS are well-poised to gain.
